text: Desmiphora lineatipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1943. It is known from Argentina.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora lineatipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1943
